snippet.title: TET - Enter the world of delicious Vietnamese food through a series of mini games!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://playables.itch.io/tet?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Prepare a meal for the Vietnamese Lunar New Year dinner. But hurry, your guests are arriving soon! A short hand-drawn experience full of delicious surprises.

TET is a fresh and colorful cooking game. Enter the world of delicious Vietnamese food through a series of mini games. Cut the tofu, wash the cabbage, delicately roll the spring rolls, and discover the secrets of the tasty recipes. 

➡️ More from Playables https://playables.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
